                                            <ol> <h3 class="title">Notas</h3> <li class="footnote " id="footnote1-13285_002_041"><a name="1-13285_002_041">&nbsp;</a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote1-13285_002_041">1.</a></span>
					<p class=""><a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.2?lang=spa#1" target="_blank">Doctrina y Convenios 93:2</a>; v&eacute;ase tambi&eacute;n <a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/nt/john/1.9?lang=spa#8" target="_blank">Juan 1:9</a>.</p>
